ai-snp5.10:1.1_0: “In whom sensual pleasures don’t stay in the realm,
ai-snp5.10:1.3_0: who has no craving for craving.
ai-snp5.10:1.4_0: he who has crossed beyond doubts,
ai-snp5.10:1.5_0: What kind of liberation is it?”
ai-snp5.10:2.1_0: “In whom sensual pleasures don’t stay in the realm,
ai-snp5.10:2.3_0: who has no craving for craving.
ai-snp5.10:2.4_0: he who has crossed beyond doubts,
ai-snp5.10:2.5_0: there is no liberation for him.”
ai-snp5.10:3.2_0: Is he wise, or is he still acquiring wisdom?
ai-snp5.10:3.3_0: I would know just what the sage is like, Sakyan:
ai-snp5.10:3.4_0: all that you come out from me.”
ai-snp5.10:4.2_0: He is wise, he is not still acquiring wisdom.
ai-snp5.10:4.3_0: Know that the Sage is just like this, Todeyya:
ai-snp5.10:4.4_0: who has nothing, and is not clinging to sense pleasures?”
ai-snp5.10:4.5_0: just as you’ll ask for new knowledge the ending of nine months.
